<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich III. Schenk von Limpurg, Hauptmann des Landfriedens zu Franken</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut um unverzügliches Kommen nach Nürnberg in einer dringlichen Angelegenheit, weshalb man Hans Camerer, Diener der Stadt, entsandt hat, und nennt als Termin kommenden Freitag; sollte der Adressat an diesem Tag nach Windsheim kommen, schickt der Rat eine Botschaft dorthin.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_124" id="60v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fridrich <expan>Schenke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Limp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l2">vnd Hauptman des lantfrids </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l3">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden voꝛmals 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l5"><expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> brief gen <expan>Limp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> geſant </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l4">geſchickt </ab></add> / vnd auch den Hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l7"><expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo / vviſʒen vvir noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l8">niht ob 
<del rend="strikethrough">d ew </del> derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener cʒu ew <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l9">oder ew 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>riten</expan> hab hat </del> fürrẏten hat / Darümb ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l10">bıten vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell 
<del rend="strikethrough">n </del> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / vnd begern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015610864_45">von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015692472_94">ew </ab></add> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinſte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015790967_116"> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> . darcʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ge </del> fügt 
<del rend="strikethrough">het </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015660319_66">
<del rend="strikethrough">wolt </del></ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ Jr </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015664510_71">vnd </ab></add> auf 
<del rend="strikethrough">den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l13">dıe <expan>nehſtk<ex>ünftige</ex></expan> </ab></add> freẏtag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l17">cʒu naht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015668089_76">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſch </del></ab></add> / hie beẏ vns 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wert </del> ſein wölt / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l16">von </ab></add> etvvaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">gar treffenlicher </del> notlicher ſache 
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015674559_81">vnd leuff </ab></add> wegen die wir mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575016368875_35"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>cʒurede<ex>n</ex></expan> heten / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575015678622_86">das wollen etc </ab></add> Moht <gap reason="illegible"/> Jr aber auf <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l23">freẏtagen naht niht her cʒu vns <expan>gereich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> do </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l24">aber auf <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeit gen winſheim kömt / So </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l25"> <expan>vvolte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> f </del> etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freunde 
<del rend="strikethrough"> auf </del> vnd <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l26">botſchaft cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> auf <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freẏtagennaht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l28">gen winſheim <expan>ſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> / die 
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_r2l27">
<del rend="strikethrough">mıt </del></ab></add> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_124_r2l32">
<add>vnd leuff</add> ercʒeln <expan>ſolte<ex>n</ex></expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_124_line_1575016558185_71"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedıg <expan>verſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab></add> <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan></del> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Galli </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_124" id="60v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Fridrich <expan>Schenke<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu <expan>Limp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        und hauptman des lantfrids </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden vormals
                                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> brief gen
                            <expan>Limp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<add>geschickt</add> und auch den Hansen <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                    <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also
                        wiszen wir noch niht, ob derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener czu ew
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist oder ew fürryten hat. Darümb so
                        biten wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz und begern von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden, daz ir <add>ew</add> durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinste <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        darczu fügt <add>und</add> auf <app>
<note><q type="date"><add>die
                                        <expan>nehstk<ex>ünftige</ex></expan></add>
                                freytag</q>19.10.1408</note>
</app> czu naht hie bey uns sein wölt <add>von</add> etwaz notlicher sache
                            <add>und leuff</add> wegen, die wir mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>czurede<ex>n</ex></expan> heten. <add>Das wollen etc.</add> Moht ir
                        aber auf <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freytagen naht niht her czu uns
                                <expan>gereich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir aber auf
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit gen Winsheim kömt, so
                                <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etlich
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> freunde und <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        botschaft czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> auf <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        freytagennaht gen Winsheim <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>, die
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache <add>und leuff</add> erczeln
                                <expan>solte<ex>n</ex></expan>. <add><expan>Ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                            gnedig <expan>vers<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan></add>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                        die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Galli. </ab></div>
</div></body>
